---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import Header from '../components/layout/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/layout/Footer.astro'
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy — LRA CloudOps" description="Privacy Policy for LRA CloudOps services." lang="en">
  <Header lang="en" />
  <section style="background:#F8F9FA;padding:3rem 1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid #DADCE0;">
    <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
      <p style="font-family:'Red Hat Text',sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:#1A73E8;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Legal</p>
      <h1 style="font-family:'Red Hat Display',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:700;color:#202124;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p style="font-family:'Red Hat Text',sans-serif;font-size:1rem;color:#5F6368;">Last updated: July 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section style="background:#FFFFFF;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;font-family:'Red Hat Text',sans-serif;font-size:1rem;color:#5F6368;line-height:1.8;">
      <h2 style="font-family:'Red Hat Display',sans-serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#202124;margin:2rem 0 1rem;">1. Who we are</h2>
      <p>LRA CloudOps is a DevOps consultancy operated by Ruben Liquenson, based in Las Palmas de Gran Canaria, Canarias, Spain. Contact: <a href="mailto:info@lracloudops.com" style="color:#1A73E8;">info@lracloudops.com</a></p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Red Hat Display',sans-serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#202124;margin:2rem 0 1rem;">2. Data we collect</h2>
      <p>When you use our contact form or request a free infrastructure audit, we collect your name, email address, GitHub repository URL (if provided), message content, and basic analytics data.</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Red Hat Display',sans-serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#202124;margin:2rem 0 1rem;">3. How we use your data</h2>
      <p>To respond to enquiries, deliver security audits, send reports by email, and improve our services. We do not sell your data or use it for advertising.</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Red Hat Display',sans-serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#202124;margin:2rem 0 1rem;">4. Third-party services</h2>
      <p>Web3Forms (forms), Resend (email), Cloudflare (hosting/analytics), Google Analytics (statistics), GitHub (repository scanning).</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Red Hat Display',sans-serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#202124;margin:2rem 0 1rem;">5. Your rights (GDPR)</h2>
      <p>You have the right to access, correct, delete or port your data. Contact <a href="mailto:info@lracloudops.com" style="color:#1A73E8;">info@lracloudops.com</a> to exercise these rights.</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Red Hat Display',sans-serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#202124;margin:2rem 0 1rem;">6. Contact</h2>
      <p><a href="mailto:info@lracloudops.com" style="color:#1A73E8;">info@lracloudops.com</a> · LRA CloudOps · Las Palmas de Gran Canaria · Spain</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <Footer lang="en" />
</Layout>
